@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Reviewed
Reviewed --> Created : review
Created --> Processing : reject
Processing --> OnHold : review
Processing : entry / log message
OnHold --> Completed : confirm
OnHold : entry / log message
Completed --> Rejected : approve
Rejected --> [*]
@enduml